tool_description: HandballAPI offers a schedule for live matches and results for top national and international leagues and tournaments. Handball World championship, handball European championship, handball Champions league, LNH Division 1, EHF European league and other leagues are all covered.

api_list.name: Search
api_list.description: This operation allows you to search for handball players, teams, and tournaments based on the search term provided.

url = "https://handballapi.p.rapidapi.com/api/handball/unique-tournament/{tournamentid}/season/{seasonid}/cuptrees"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "handballapi.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
